.TH XIL\-CSV\-JOIN "1" "2026\-04\-24" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-csv\-join
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-csv\-join
[-h] (--episode EPISODE | --tag TAG) [--show SHOW] [--csv CSV_PATH] [--sfx SFX_PATH] [--cast CAST_PATH] [--output OUT_PATH]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Annotate a parsed episode CSV with SFX and cast config data.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,EPISODE\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S02E03) — derives default input/output paths

.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Raw tag for non\-episodic content (e.g. V01C03, D01)

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-csv\fR \fI\,CSV_PATH\/\fR
Override input CSV path

.TP
\fB\-\-sfx\fR \fI\,SFX_PATH\/\fR
Override SFX JSON path

.TP
\fB\-\-cast\fR \fI\,CAST_PATH\/\fR
Override cast JSON path

.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI\,OUT_PATH\/\fR
Override output CSV path

